                            <comment id="17759672" author="houston" created="Mon, 28 Aug 2023 17:32:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for finding this &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=hossman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;hossman&quot;&gt;hossman&lt;/a&gt; , I think it&apos;s &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16825&quot; title=&quot;Generate Java bindings from OpenAPI spec&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-16825&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-16825&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; because the BackupDeletionData class is not serializing correctly. But it&apos;s amazing how much it looks like this Jira is the culprit. I&apos;ll investigate more and try to fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
